headline: Fifth Third Again Named Among ‘World’s Most Admired Companies™’ by Fortune Magazine
summary: CINCINNATI, January 29, 2025--For the second consecutive year, Fifth Third (NASDAQ: FITB) has been named among the World’s Most Admired Companies™ by Fortune Magazine.
